# Layout & Spacing

## Page Container
- Padding: `px-[32px] pt-[12px] pb-[32px]`, BG: `bg-white`, `min-h-full`

## Edge-to-Edge Separators
```tsx
<div className="w-[calc(100%+64px)] h-[1px] bg-[#e0e0e0] mx-[-32px]" />
```

## Border Radius
- Default: 8px, Card: 12px, Large cards: `rounded-[20px]`, Button: `rounded-[8px]`

## Shadows
- `shadow-elevation-sm` → `0 8px 16px rgba(16,16,16,0.07)` — use sparingly

## Primary Filter (Default)
- Vertical layout: label on top, value below, no border on trigger
- Label: `text-[12px] text-[#7e7e7e] uppercase tracking-[0.6px] font-semibold`
- Value: `text-[14px] text-[#101010] font-semibold`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`, ChevronDown rotates 180deg when open
- Dropdown: `bg-white border rounded-lg shadow-lg z-10`

## Unified Search Widget
- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-lg h-[40px] w-[560px] overflow-hidden ml-auto`
- Left: type dropdown, vertical divider, right: search input with icon
- Dynamic placeholder based on selected filter type

## Pagination
- Left: `PAGE 1 OF 32` in `text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
- Right: Prev/Next buttons with `bg-white border rounded-lg px-4 py-2 font-semibold`
